{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "22.1", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "text_original": "今天下之士君子，知小而不知大。", "text_normalized": "今天下之士君子，知小而不知大。", "canonical_ref": "22.2", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "text_original": "何以知之？", "text_normalized": "何以知之？", "canonical_ref": "22.3", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "text_original": "以其處家者知之。", "text_normalized": "以其處家者知之。", "canonical_ref": "22.4", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "text_original": "若處家得罪於家長，猶有鄰家所避逃之。", "text_normalized": "若處家得罪於家長，猶有鄰家所避逃之。", "canonical_ref": "22.5", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "text_original": "然且親戚、兄弟、所知識，共相儆戒，皆曰：", "text_normalized": "然且親戚、兄弟、所知識，共相儆戒，皆曰：", "canonical_ref": "22.6", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 7, "text_original": "「不可不戒矣！", "text_normalized": "「不可不戒矣！", "canonical_ref": "22.7", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 8, "text_original": "不可不慎矣！", "text_normalized": "不可不慎矣！", "canonical_ref": "22.8", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 9, "text_original": "惡有處家而得罪於家長而可為也？", "text_normalized": "惡有處家而得罪於家長而可為也？", "canonical_ref": "22.9", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 10, "text_original": "」非獨處家者為然，雖處國亦然。", "text_normalized": "」非獨處家者為然，雖處國亦然。", "canonical_ref": "22.10", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 11, "text_original": "處國得罪於國君，猶有鄰國所避逃之。", "text_normalized": "處國得罪於國君，猶有鄰國所避逃之。", "canonical_ref": "22.11", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 12, "text_original": "然且親戚兄弟所知識，共相儆戒，皆曰：", "text_normalized": "然且親戚兄弟所知識，共相儆戒，皆曰：", "canonical_ref": "22.12", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 13, "text_original": "「不可不戒矣！", "text_normalized": "「不可不戒矣！", "canonical_ref": "22.13", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 14, "text_original": "不可不慎矣！", "text_normalized": "不可不慎矣！", "canonical_ref": "22.14", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 15, "text_original": "誰亦有處國得罪於國君而可為也？", "text_normalized": "誰亦有處國得罪於國君而可為也？", "canonical_ref": "22.15", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 16, "text_original": "」此有所避逃之者也，相儆戒猶若此其厚。", "text_normalized": "」此有所避逃之者也，相儆戒猶若此其厚。", "canonical_ref": "22.16", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 17, "text_original": "況無所避逃之者，相儆戒豈不愈厚，然後可哉？", "text_normalized": "況無所避逃之者，相儆戒豈不愈厚，然後可哉？", "canonical_ref": "22.17", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 18, "text_original": "且語言有之曰：", "text_normalized": "且語言有之曰：", "canonical_ref": "22.18", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 19, "text_original": "「焉而晏日，焉天得罪，將惡避逃之？", "text_normalized": "「焉而晏日，焉天得罪，將惡避逃之？", "canonical_ref": "22.19", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 20, "text_original": "」曰：", "text_normalized": "」曰：", "canonical_ref": "22.20", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 21, "text_original": "無所避逃之。", "text_normalized": "無所避逃之。", "canonical_ref": "22.21", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 22, "text_original": "夫天，不可為林谷幽門無人，明必見之。", "text_normalized": "夫天，不可為林谷幽門無人，明必見之。", "canonical_ref": "22.22", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 23, "text_original": "然而天下之士君子之於天也，忽然不知以相儆戒。", "text_normalized": "然而天下之士君子之於天也，忽然不知以相儆戒。", "canonical_ref": "22.23", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 24, "text_original": "此我所以知天下士君子知小而不知大也。", "text_normalized": "此我所以知天下士君子知小而不知大也。", "canonical_ref": "22.24", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 25, "text_original": "然則天亦何欲何惡？", "text_normalized": "然則天亦何欲何惡？", "canonical_ref": "22.25", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0026", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 26, "text_original": "天欲義而惡不義。", "text_normalized": "天欲義而惡不義。", "canonical_ref": "22.26", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0027", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 27, "text_original": "然則率天下之百姓以從事於義，則我乃為天之所欲也。", "text_normalized": "然則率天下之百姓以從事於義，則我乃為天之所欲也。", "canonical_ref": "22.27", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0028", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 28, "text_original": "我為天之所欲，天亦為我所欲。", "text_normalized": "我為天之所欲，天亦為我所欲。", "canonical_ref": "22.28", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0029", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 29, "text_original": "然則我何欲何惡？", "text_normalized": "然則我何欲何惡？", "canonical_ref": "22.29", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0030", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 30, "text_original": "我欲福祿而惡禍祟。", "text_normalized": "我欲福祿而惡禍祟。", "canonical_ref": "22.30", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0031", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 31, "text_original": "若我不為天之所欲，而為天之所不欲，然則我率天下之百姓以從事於禍祟中也。", "text_normalized": "若我不為天之所欲，而為天之所不欲，然則我率天下之百姓以從事於禍祟中也。", "canonical_ref": "22.31", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0032", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 32, "text_original": "然則何以知天之欲義而惡不義？", "text_normalized": "然則何以知天之欲義而惡不義？", "canonical_ref": "22.32", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0033", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 33, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "22.33", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0034", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 34, "text_original": "天下有義則生，無義則死。", "text_normalized": "天下有義則生，無義則死。", "canonical_ref": "22.34", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0035", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 35, "text_original": "有義則富，無義則貧。", "text_normalized": "有義則富，無義則貧。", "canonical_ref": "22.35", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0036", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 36, "text_original": "有義則治，無義則亂。", "text_normalized": "有義則治，無義則亂。", "canonical_ref": "22.36", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0037", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 37, "text_original": "然則天欲其生而惡其死，欲其富而惡其貧，欲其治而惡其亂。", "text_normalized": "然則天欲其生而惡其死，欲其富而惡其貧，欲其治而惡其亂。", "canonical_ref": "22.37", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0038", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 38, "text_original": "此我所以知天欲義而惡不義也。", "text_normalized": "此我所以知天欲義而惡不義也。", "canonical_ref": "22.38", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0039", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 39, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "22.39", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0040", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 40, "text_original": "且夫義者，政也。", "text_normalized": "且夫義者，政也。", "canonical_ref": "22.40", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0041", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 41, "text_original": "無從下之政上，必從上之政下。", "text_normalized": "無從下之政上，必從上之政下。", "canonical_ref": "22.41", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0042", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 42, "text_original": "是故庶人竭力從事，未得次己而為政，有士政之。", "text_normalized": "是故庶人竭力從事，未得次己而為政，有士政之。", "canonical_ref": "22.42", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0043", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 43, "text_original": "士竭力從事，未得次己而為政，有將軍、大夫政之。", "text_normalized": "士竭力從事，未得次己而為政，有將軍、大夫政之。", "canonical_ref": "22.43", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0044", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 44, "text_original": "將軍、大夫竭力從事，未得次己而為政，有三公、諸侯政之。", "text_normalized": "將軍、大夫竭力從事，未得次己而為政，有三公、諸侯政之。", "canonical_ref": "22.44", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0045", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 45, "text_original": "三公、諸侯竭力聽治，未得次己而為政，有天子政之。", "text_normalized": "三公、諸侯竭力聽治，未得次己而為政，有天子政之。", "canonical_ref": "22.45", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0046", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 46, "text_original": "天子未得次己而為政，有天政之。", "text_normalized": "天子未得次己而為政，有天政之。", "canonical_ref": "22.46", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0047", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 47, "text_original": "天子為政於三公、諸侯、士、庶人，天下之士君子固明知，天之為政於天子，天下百姓未得之明知也。", "text_normalized": "天子為政於三公、諸侯、士、庶人，天下之士君子固明知，天之為政於天子，天下百姓未得之明知也。", "canonical_ref": "22.47", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0048", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 48, "text_original": "故昔三代聖王禹、湯、文、武，欲以天之為政於天子，明說天下之百姓，故莫不犓牛羊，豢犬彘，潔為粢盛酒醴，以祭祀上帝鬼神，而求祈福於天。", "text_normalized": "故昔三代聖王禹、湯、文、武，欲以天之為政於天子，明說天下之百姓，故莫不犓牛羊，豢犬彘，潔為粢盛酒醴，以祭祀上帝鬼神，而求祈福於天。", "canonical_ref": "22.48", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0049", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 49, "text_original": "我未嘗聞天下之所求祈福於天子者也，我所以知天之為政於天子者也。", "text_normalized": "我未嘗聞天下之所求祈福於天子者也，我所以知天之為政於天子者也。", "canonical_ref": "22.49", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0050", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 50, "text_original": "故天子者，天下之窮貴也，天下之窮富也。", "text_normalized": "故天子者，天下之窮貴也，天下之窮富也。", "canonical_ref": "22.50", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0051", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 51, "text_original": "故於富且貴者，當天意而不可不順。", "text_normalized": "故於富且貴者，當天意而不可不順。", "canonical_ref": "22.51", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0052", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 52, "text_original": "順天意者，兼相愛，交相利，必得賞。", "text_normalized": "順天意者，兼相愛，交相利，必得賞。", "canonical_ref": "22.52", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0053", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 53, "text_original": "反天意者，別相惡，交相賊，必得罰。", "text_normalized": "反天意者，別相惡，交相賊，必得罰。", "canonical_ref": "22.53", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0054", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 54, "text_original": "然則是誰順天意而得賞者？", "text_normalized": "然則是誰順天意而得賞者？", "canonical_ref": "22.54", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0055", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 55, "text_original": "誰反天意而得罰者？", "text_normalized": "誰反天意而得罰者？", "canonical_ref": "22.55", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0056", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 56, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "22.56", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0057", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 57, "text_original": "昔三代聖王禹、湯、文、武，此順天意而得賞也，昔三代之暴王桀、紂、幽、厲，此反天意而得罰者也。", "text_normalized": "昔三代聖王禹、湯、文、武，此順天意而得賞也，昔三代之暴王桀、紂、幽、厲，此反天意而得罰者也。", "canonical_ref": "22.57", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0058", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 58, "text_original": "然則禹、湯、文、武，其得賞何以也？", "text_normalized": "然則禹、湯、文、武，其得賞何以也？", "canonical_ref": "22.58", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0059", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 59, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "22.59", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0060", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 60, "text_original": "其事上尊天，中事鬼神，下愛人，故天意曰：", "text_normalized": "其事上尊天，中事鬼神，下愛人，故天意曰：", "canonical_ref": "22.60", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0061", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 61, "text_original": "「此之我所愛，兼而愛之；", "text_normalized": "「此之我所愛，兼而愛之；", "canonical_ref": "22.61", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0062", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 62, "text_original": "我所利，兼而利之。", "text_normalized": "我所利，兼而利之。", "canonical_ref": "22.62", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0063", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 63, "text_original": "愛人者此為博焉，利人者此為厚焉。", "text_normalized": "愛人者此為博焉，利人者此為厚焉。", "canonical_ref": "22.63", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0064", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 64, "text_original": "」故使貴為天子，富有天下，業萬世子孫。", "text_normalized": "」故使貴為天子，富有天下，業萬世子孫。", "canonical_ref": "22.64", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0065", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 65, "text_original": "傳稱其善，方施天下，至今稱之，謂之聖王。", "text_normalized": "傳稱其善，方施天下，至今稱之，謂之聖王。", "canonical_ref": "22.65", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0066", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 66, "text_original": "然則桀、紂、幽、厲，得其罰何以也？", "text_normalized": "然則桀、紂、幽、厲，得其罰何以也？", "canonical_ref": "22.66", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0067", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 67, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "22.67", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0068", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 68, "text_original": "其事上詬天，中詬鬼，下賊人。", "text_normalized": "其事上詬天，中詬鬼，下賊人。", "canonical_ref": "22.68", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0069", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 69, "text_original": "故天意曰：", "text_normalized": "故天意曰：", "canonical_ref": "22.69", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0070", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 70, "text_original": "「此之我所愛，別而惡之；", "text_normalized": "「此之我所愛，別而惡之；", "canonical_ref": "22.70", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0071", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 71, "text_original": "我所利，交而賊之。", "text_normalized": "我所利，交而賊之。", "canonical_ref": "22.71", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0072", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 72, "text_original": "惡人者，此為之博也；", "text_normalized": "惡人者，此為之博也；", "canonical_ref": "22.72", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0073", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 73, "text_original": "賊人者，此為之厚也。", "text_normalized": "賊人者，此為之厚也。", "canonical_ref": "22.73", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0074", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 74, "text_original": "」故使不得終其壽，不歿其世，至今毀之，謂之暴王。", "text_normalized": "」故使不得終其壽，不歿其世，至今毀之，謂之暴王。", "canonical_ref": "22.74", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0075", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 75, "text_original": "然則何以知天之愛天下之百姓？", "text_normalized": "然則何以知天之愛天下之百姓？", "canonical_ref": "22.75", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0076", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 76, "text_original": "以其兼而明之。", "text_normalized": "以其兼而明之。", "canonical_ref": "22.76", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0077", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 77, "text_original": "何以知其兼而明之？", "text_normalized": "何以知其兼而明之？", "canonical_ref": "22.77", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0078", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 78, "text_original": "以其兼而有之。", "text_normalized": "以其兼而有之。", "canonical_ref": "22.78", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0079", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 79, "text_original": "何以知其兼而有之？", "text_normalized": "何以知其兼而有之？", "canonical_ref": "22.79", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0080", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 80, "text_original": "以其兼而食焉。", "text_normalized": "以其兼而食焉。", "canonical_ref": "22.80", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0081", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 81, "text_original": "何以知其兼而食焉？", "text_normalized": "何以知其兼而食焉？", "canonical_ref": "22.81", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0082", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 82, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "22.82", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0083", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 83, "text_original": "四海之內，粒食之民，莫不犓牛羊，豢犬彘，潔為粢盛酒醴，以祭祀於上帝鬼神。", "text_normalized": "四海之內，粒食之民，莫不犓牛羊，豢犬彘，潔為粢盛酒醴，以祭祀於上帝鬼神。", "canonical_ref": "22.83", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0084", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 84, "text_original": "天有邑人，何用弗愛也？", "text_normalized": "天有邑人，何用弗愛也？", "canonical_ref": "22.84", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0085", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 85, "text_original": "且吾言殺一不辜者，必有一不祥。", "text_normalized": "且吾言殺一不辜者，必有一不祥。", "canonical_ref": "22.85", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0086", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 86, "text_original": "殺不辜者誰也？", "text_normalized": "殺不辜者誰也？", "canonical_ref": "22.86", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0087", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 87, "text_original": "則人也。", "text_normalized": "則人也。", "canonical_ref": "22.87", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0088", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 88, "text_original": "予之不祥者誰也？", "text_normalized": "予之不祥者誰也？", "canonical_ref": "22.88", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0089", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 89, "text_original": "則天也。", "text_normalized": "則天也。", "canonical_ref": "22.89", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0090", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 90, "text_original": "若以天為不愛天下之百姓，則何故以人與人相殺，而天予之不祥？", "text_normalized": "若以天為不愛天下之百姓，則何故以人與人相殺，而天予之不祥？", "canonical_ref": "22.90", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0091", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 91, "text_original": "此我所以知天之愛天下之百姓也。", "text_normalized": "此我所以知天之愛天下之百姓也。", "canonical_ref": "22.91", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0092", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 92, "text_original": "順天意者，義政也。", "text_normalized": "順天意者，義政也。", "canonical_ref": "22.92", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0093", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 93, "text_original": "反天意者，力政也。", "text_normalized": "反天意者，力政也。", "canonical_ref": "22.93", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0094", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 94, "text_original": "然義政將奈何哉？", "text_normalized": "然義政將奈何哉？", "canonical_ref": "22.94", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0095", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 95, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "22.95", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0096", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 96, "text_original": "處大國不攻小國，處大家不篡小家，強者不劫弱，貴者不傲賤，多詐者不欺愚。", "text_normalized": "處大國不攻小國，處大家不篡小家，強者不劫弱，貴者不傲賤，多詐者不欺愚。", "canonical_ref": "22.96", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0097", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 97, "text_original": "此必上利於天，中利於鬼，下利於人。", "text_normalized": "此必上利於天，中利於鬼，下利於人。", "canonical_ref": "22.97", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0098", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 98, "text_original": "三利無所不利，故舉天下美名加之，謂之聖王。", "text_normalized": "三利無所不利，故舉天下美名加之，謂之聖王。", "canonical_ref": "22.98", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0099", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 99, "text_original": "力政者則與此異，言非此，行反此，猶倖馳也。", "text_normalized": "力政者則與此異，言非此，行反此，猶倖馳也。", "canonical_ref": "22.99", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0100", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 100, "text_original": "處大國攻小國，處大家篡小家，強者劫弱，貴者傲賤，多詐欺愚。", "text_normalized": "處大國攻小國，處大家篡小家，強者劫弱，貴者傲賤，多詐欺愚。", "canonical_ref": "22.100", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0101", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 101, "text_original": "此上不利於天，中不利於鬼，下不利於人。", "text_normalized": "此上不利於天，中不利於鬼，下不利於人。", "canonical_ref": "22.101", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0102", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 102, "text_original": "三不利無所利，故舉天下惡名加之，謂之暴王。", "text_normalized": "三不利無所利，故舉天下惡名加之，謂之暴王。", "canonical_ref": "22.102", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0103", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 103, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "22.103", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0104", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 104, "text_original": "我有天志，譬若輪人之有規，匠人之有矩。", "text_normalized": "我有天志，譬若輪人之有規，匠人之有矩。", "canonical_ref": "22.104", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0105", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 105, "text_original": "輪匠執其規矩，以度天下之方圓，曰：", "text_normalized": "輪匠執其規矩，以度天下之方圓，曰：", "canonical_ref": "22.105", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0106", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 106, "text_original": "「中者是也，不中者非也。", "text_normalized": "「中者是也，不中者非也。", "canonical_ref": "22.106", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0107", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 107, "text_original": "」今天下之士君子之書，不可勝載，言語不可盡計，上說諸侯，下說列士，其於仁義則大相遠也。", "text_normalized": "」今天下之士君子之書，不可勝載，言語不可盡計，上說諸侯，下說列士，其於仁義則大相遠也。", "canonical_ref": "22.107", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0108", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 108, "text_original": "何以知之？", "text_normalized": "何以知之？", "canonical_ref": "22.108", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0109", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 109, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "22.109", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0110", "section_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i", "source_id": "mozi-022-will-of-heaven-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 110, "text_original": "我得天下之明法以度之。", "text_normalized": "我得天下之明法以度之。", "canonical_ref": "22.110", "notes": ""}
